Starting the container

On the RHEL 7 Host :
Running
	modprobe dm-multipath non host
	docker run --rm --privileged --net=host -ti -e 'container=docker' -v /proc/modules:/proc/modules -v /var/lib/libvirt/:/var/lib/libvirt/ -v /sys/fs/cgroup:/sys/fs/cgroup:rw vdsmc

Building
	docker build -t vdsmc .


Testing
	Checking libvirt
		virsh --connect qemu+tcp://<docker host>/system list --all

Connectiong to docker container

	docker inspect --format {{.State.Pid}} <container_name_or_ID>
 	nsenter  --mount --uts --net --pid --ipc --target <container pid from previos command>
